.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-FEE-REVENUE-ESTIMATE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-fee-revenue-estimate \- FEAT-2510 estimated fee revenue across all channels
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-fee-revenue-estimate
.SH DESCRIPTION
channel-fee-revenue-estimate for lightning CLI (FEAT-2510).
.PP
Returns the estimated fee revenue as the sum of fee_base_msat plus fee_proportional_millionths times capacity divided by 1,000,000 for each channel.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
